Given a number as string(n) , find the remainder of the number whe it is divided by 7

Example 1:

Input:
9
Output:
2

*****************CODE***************
int remainderWith7(string n)
    {
        //Your code here
        int ans=0;
        for(int i=0;i<n.size();i++)
        {
            ans=ans*10 + int(n[i] - '0');                     //ans=ans*10 + (n[i] - '0')        is also correct
            ans=ans%7;
        }
         return ans;
    }



